case_circumstances: At about 1553 hrs on 4/7/2011, the owner of a private residence  was walking on his property with a plumber/friend when they went over to a garage at the back of the property.  When they entered the small portion of the garage, they noted a foul odor.  They moved a white blanket and discovered the decedent in a state of decomposition. DC Fire/EMS responded and departed after finding no signs of life
